Score Media and Gaming Inc. (“
theScore
,” “
Us
,” or “
We
”) Privacy Policy outlines the collection, use, processing and disclosure of your personal information. This Privacy Policy applies to theScore’s and its associated affiliates’ (“
we
,” “
our
” or “
us
”) websites and any mobile application of ours (each, an “
App
”) (collectively, the “
Service
”), unless otherwise indicated.
