To provide you with all of the requested Service, we collect and process the following categories of personal information:
Identifiers
, such as your first and last name, postal address, email address, telephone number, date of birth, gender identity, age, or advertising identifiers associated with your device, which may be provided by the operating system of your device.
Messages, Comments, and other User-Generated Content
that you choose to provide to us voluntarily, including comments, messages, and other content you post to the Service.
